<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Electrical Engineering - GoFarAsYouCan</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
      /* Base Styles */
      :root {
  --primary-color: #1f1d2b;        /* Deep charcoal */
  --primary-light: #3b3756;        /* Slightly lighter charcoal */
  --secondary-color: #181e34;      /* Rich slate blue */
  --accent-color: #ff6b81;         /* Vibrant coral pink */
  --accent-light: #ffaec0;         /* Soft pink */
  --text-color: #f1f1f1;           /* Light gray for readability */
  --light-text: #ffffff;           /* White text */
  --light-bg: #2e303e;             /* Soft slate background */
  --dark-bg: #18171f;              /* True dark background */
  --card-bg: #2a2a3c;              /* Elegant card background */
  --border-radius: 10px;
  --box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  --transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }

* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--text-color);
  background-color: var(--light-bg);
  background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light-bg) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
  background-attachment: fixed;
}

.container {
  width: 90%;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 20px;
}

a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--accent-light);
  transition: var(--transition);
}

a:hover {
  color: #e0aaff;
}

img {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
}

.bg-light {
  background-color: var(--primary-light);
  background-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-light), var(--secondary-color));
}

/* Navbar */
.navbar {
  background-color: var(--dark-bg);
  color: var(--light-text);
  padding: 1rem 0;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 1000;
  box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
}

.navbar .container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: var(--light-text);
}

.back-button a {
  color: var(--light-text);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
}

.back-button a:hover {
  color: var(--accent-light);
}

/* Hero Section */
.hero {
  background-color: var(--dark-bg);
  color: var(--light-text);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 6rem 0;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);
}

.hero .overlay {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  opacity: 0.2;
  mix-blend-mode: luminosity;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  position: relative;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.hero p {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
}

/* Section Styles */
.section {
  padding: 5rem 0;
}

.section-title {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  color: var(--accent-light);
  position: relative;
  font-size: 2rem;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

.section-title::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -10px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 80px;
  height: 4px;
  background-color: var(--accent-light);
  border-radius: 2px;
}

.section-intro {
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

/* Content Wrapper */
.content-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2.5rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.text-content {
  flex: 1;
}

.text-content p {
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}

.image-content {
  flex: 1;
  box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Cards Grid */
.cards-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.two-columns {
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(450px, 1fr));
}

.three-columns {
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
}

.four-columns {
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
}

/* Card Styles */
.card {
  background-color: var(--card-bg);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  transition: var(--transition);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  border-color: var(--accent-light);
}

.card-header {
  padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 0.5rem;
  background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.3), rgba(199, 125, 255, 0.3));
}

.card-header h3 {
  color: var(--accent-light);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

.card-header h3 i {
  color: var(--accent-light);
}

.card-header p {
  color: #ccc;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.card-content {
  padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem;
}

/* Project Cards */
.project-card .card-image {
  height: 180px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.project-card .card-image img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}

.project-card:hover .card-image img {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Career List */
.career-list {
  list-style: none;
}

.career-list li {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0.5rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.career-list li:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.badge {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  color: #ecf0f1;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
  border-radius: 9999px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.badge.top {
  background-color: var(--accent-color);
  color: white;
}

.badge.program {
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: white;
}

.growth-sectors {
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

.text-success {
  color: #c77dff;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}

/* Education Pathways */
.education-pathways {
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  background-color: var(--card-bg);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.education-pathways h3 {
  color: var(--accent-light);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
}

.pathways-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
}

.pathway-card {
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding: 1rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  transition: var(--transition);
}

.pathway-card:hover {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border-color: var(--accent-light);
}

.pathway-card h4 {
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

/* Skills List */
.skills-list {
  list-style: none;
}

.skills-list li {
  padding: 0.5rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.skills-list li:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.skill-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.skill-desc {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #bdc3c7;
}

/* Accordion */
.accordion {
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.accordion-item {
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.accordion-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.accordion-header {
  padding: 1rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-weight: 600;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  transition: var(--transition);
}

.accordion-header::after {
  content: '\f078';
  font-family: 'Font Awesome 5 Free';
  font-weight: 900;
  transition: var(--transition);
}

.accordion-header.active::after {
  transform: rotate(180deg);
}

.accordion-content {
  padding: 0 1rem;
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
}

.accordion-content p {
  padding-bottom: 1rem;
}

.accordion-item.active .accordion-header {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  color: var(--accent-light);
}

.accordion-item.active .accordion-content {
  max-height: 500px;
}

/* Specialization Grid */
.specialization-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.specialization-card {
  background-color: var(--card-bg);
  padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  text-align: center;
  transition: var(--transition);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  color: var(--text-color);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.specialization-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  background-color: var(--primary-color);
  color: var(--light-text);
  border-color: var(--accent-light);
}

.specialization-card i {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: var(--accent-light);
  transition: var(--transition);
}

.specialization-card:hover i {
  color: var(--light-text);
}

.specialization-card h3 {
  font-size: 1rem;
}

/* Internship List */
.internship-list {
  list-style: none;
}

.internship-list li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.company-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.company-desc {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #bdc3c7;
}

/* Internship Tips */
.internship-tips {
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  background-color: var(--primary-light);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.internship-tips h3 {
  color: var(--accent-light);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
}

.tips-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
  list-style: none;
}

.tips-grid li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.tip-number {
  background-color: var(--dark-bg);
  width: 2rem;
  height: 2rem;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--accent-light);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.tip-title {
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.tip-desc {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #bdc3c7;
}

/* Tabs */
.tabs {
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.tab-buttons {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.tab-button {
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  background-color: var(--dark-bg);
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: var(--transition);
  color: var(--text-color);
}

.tab-button:first-child {
  border-radius: var(--border-radius) 0 0 var(--border-radius);
}

.tab-button:last-child {
  border-radius: 0 var(--border-radius) var(--border-radius) 0;
}

.tab-button.active {
  background-color: var(--accent-color);
  color: var(--light-text);
}

.tab-content {
  display: none;
}

.tab-content.active {
  display: block;
}

/* Colleges Grid */
.colleges-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.college-card {
  background-color: var(--card-bg);
  padding: 1.25rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  transition: var(--transition);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.college-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  border-color: var(--accent-light);
}

.college-card h3 {
  color: var(--accent-light);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.college-location {
  color: #bdc3c7;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.college-details {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  color: #bdc3c7;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.college-rank, .college-year {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

.college-rank i {
  color: var(--accent-light);
}

.college-year i {
  color: #3498db;
}

.college-info {
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding-top: 1rem;
}

.college-info p {
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.college-info span {
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* FAQ Section */
.faq-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
  background-color: var(--dark-bg);
  color: var(--light-text);
  padding: 4rem 0 1rem;
  background-image: linear-gradient(to top, var(--dark-bg), var(--primary-light));
}

.footer-content {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}

.footer-logo h2 {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.footer-links h3,
.footer-resources h3 {
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  display: inline-block;
}

.footer-links h3::after,
.footer-resources h3::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 50px;
  height: 3px;
  background-color: var(--accent-light);
}

.footer-links ul,
.footer-resources ul {
  list-style-type: none;
}

.footer-links li,
.footer-resources li {
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.footer-links a,
.footer-resources a {
  color: #bdc3c7;
}

.footer-links a:hover,
.footer-resources a:hover {
  color: var(--accent-light);
}

.footer-bottom {
  text-align: center;
  padding-top: 1.25rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 992px) {
  .content-wrapper {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .two-columns {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .section {
    padding: 3.5rem 0;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .college-details {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 576px) {
  .navbar {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tab-buttons {
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }

  .tab-button {
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .tab-button:first-child {
    border-radius: var(--border-radius) var(--border-radius) 0 0;
  }

  .tab-button:last-child {
    border-radius: 0 0 var(--border-radius) var(--border-radius);
  }

  .specialization-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
  }
}
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">GoFarAsYouCan</div>
            <div class="back-button">
                <a href="/Engineering/engineering.ejs"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Electrical Engineering</h1>
            <p>Explore the world of electricity, electronics, and power systems that drive modern technology and innovation</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- What is Electrical Engineering Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Electrical Engineering?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Electrical engineering is a field focused on the study and application of electricity, electronics, and electromagnetism. It encompasses the design, development, testing, and supervision of electrical systems and equipment ranging from tiny microchips to massive power generation systems.</p>
                    <p>As an electrical engineer, you'll work with technologies that power our world, from renewable energy systems and electric vehicles to telecommunications networks and consumer electronics. The field combines principles of physics and mathematics with practical engineering skills to solve complex problems.</p>
                    <p>Electrical engineering plays a crucial role in addressing global challenges in energy efficiency, sustainable power generation, automation, and the development of smart technologies that enhance our daily lives.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Specializations Section -->
    <section class="section bg-light" id="specializations">
      <div class="container">
          <h2 class="section-title">Specializations</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Discover diverse specializations within electrical engineering that align with your interests and career aspirations:</p>
          
          <div class="specialization-grid">
              <a href="power.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                  <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                  <h3>Power Systems</h3>
              </a>
              <a href="electronics.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                  <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
                  <h3>Electronics</h3>
              </a>
              <a href="control.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                  <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
                  <h3>Control Systems</h3>
              </a>
              <a href="telecommunication.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                  <i class="fas fa-satellite-dish"></i>
                  <h3>Telecommunications</h3>
              </a>
              <a href="signal.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                  <i class="fas fa-wave-square"></i>
                  <h3>Signal Processing</h3>
              </a>
              <a href="embedded.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                  <i class="fas fa-memory"></i>
                  <h3>Embedded Systems</h3>
              </a>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>

    <!-- Career Paths Section -->
    <section class="section bg-light" id="careers">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Career Paths & Outlook</h2>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Industry Roles</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <ul class="career-list">
                            <li>
                                <span>Power Systems Engineer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹5-15 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span>Electronics Engineer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹6-18 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span>Control Systems Engineer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹7-20 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span>Embedded Systems Developer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹8-22 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Job Outlook</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>The demand for electrical engineers in India is projected to grow by 15% through 2030, with over 40,000 new positions annually.</p>
                        <div class="growth-sectors">
                            <span class="text-success">Growth Sectors:</span>
                            <ul>
                                <li>• Renewable Energy</li>
                                <li>• Electric Vehicles</li>
                                <li>• IoT & Smart Devices</li>
                                <li>• Automation & Robotics</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-award"></i> Certifications</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>• Professional Engineer (PE) License</li>
                            <li>• Certified Electrical Safety Professional</li>
                            <li>• CCNA (Cisco Certified Network Associate)</li>
                            <li>• CompTIA A+ Certification</li>
                            <li>• PLC Programming Certification</li>
                            <li>• Power Systems Protection Certification</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="education-pathways">
                <h3>Higher Education Pathways</h3>
                <div class="pathways-grid">
                    <div class="pathway-card">
